========================================================================
=  README for ex12: four_in_a_row.py, communicator.py, game.py, ai.py  =
========================================================================


==================
=  Description:  =
==================
Exercise Goal:
 Creating a GUI for a game, with an option for AI gameplay, while setting a
 Server and a Client and establishing communication between two computers.


======================
=  Special Comments  =
======================

The GUI makes use of graphics created especially for it. In order the run the
game properly, the attached folder "graphics" MUST be located at the same
folder with the "four_in_a_row.py" file.

~ We used stackoverflow.com to learn about GUI and communication.
